high_descs: Walk across the room around the chair and coffee table to the couch with a cardboard box and a pillow on it, continue until you are facing the red pillow at the end of the couch.
Pick up the watering can that is on the ground to the right of the couch.
Turn around and walk around the coffee table to the black desk.
Place the the watering can on the black desk opposite the side where the chair is pulled in.
anns.task_desc: Move a watering can onto the black desk.

high_descs: Turn right and walk around the sofa chair, walk to the corner with plants
Take the pot by the plant
Turn around and walk to the black office table
Put the pot on the table
anns.task_desc: Move the pot from the corner with the plant to the black office table

high_descs: Move to the plant in the corner next to the couch.
Pick up the white water can from the floor.
Bring he water can to the black desk.
Put the water can on the black desk.
anns.task_desc: Put a white water can on the black desk.
